# Never commit secrets or local-only state.
# Ignore the folder CONTENTS (not the folder itself, so the whitelist below
# works — a trailing-slash `99-SECRETS/` would exclude the dir and kill the
# negations, leaving the scaffold untracked).
99-SECRETS/*
!99-SECRETS/.gitkeep
!99-SECRETS/README.md
!99-SECRETS/secrets-registry.md
# archive/ (the encrypted .gpg vault) stays ignored: created on first secret.
99-SECRETS/archive/

# Deploy secrets
03-INFRA/deploy/.env

# Python noise (scripts generate this on run)
__pycache__/
*.pyc

# OS/editor noise
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
*.swp
*.swo
*~
.idea/
.vscode/
